{"tid":583843,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"比着你地會想返邊份？","createTime":"2018-03-07T10:42:04.000Z","updateTime":"2018-03-07T16:47:18.000Z","uid":147789,"like":4,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"1b30d28c17140502cadae714d76ea129dbd9c878","tid":583843,"uid":147789,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-07T10:42:04.000Z","msg":"返緊兩份兼職<br />\n<br />\n一份無名零售業 要早一個星期報更<br />\n有時唔想返可以直接唔報更都ok<br />\n平時好hea可以成日吹水 <br />\n同啲同事幾熟 又會一齊hea<br />\n不過有貨嚟就比較勞力<br />\n低到38蚊時薪 一至兩個月加一蚊<br />\n<br />\n另一份係返狗會跑馬日電話投注<br />\n返星期三 六/日<br />\n識唔到人 極悶 口乾 得閒比啲hihi阿叔屌兩句<br />\n精神虐待<br />\n58蚊時薪<br />\n<br />\n到底繼續返兩份定點樣好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n想儲定錢<br />\n利串垃圾hd仔"},{"pid":"a11766388b2afaba4189e759a00117be4a543eda","tid":583843,"uid":7729,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-07T10:48:56.000Z","msg":"搵過第份"},{"pid":"883809256531c25d271710792347ed842ac65677","tid":583843,"uid":147789,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"a11766388b2afaba4189e759a00117be4a543eda","tid":583843,"uid":7729,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-07T10:48:56.000Z","msg":"搵過第份"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-07T11:36:42.000Z","msg":"兩份都唔返？<br />\n有冇啲咩好工推薦下<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f9d22427c70366a95d2abc29732f1f8eb31441e2","tid":583843,"uid":18607,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-07T11:37:56.000Z","msg":"我都想返9會"},{"pid":"95efa778b101698e1e8110feb652c575e63b52bb","tid":583843,"uid":53413,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-07T11:40:22.000Z","msg":"零售業啦<br />\n返工求開心 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"193c9a5bce6b1072848e06bb6edc7c834393d7b7","tid":583843,"uid":147789,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"f9d22427c70366a95d2abc29732f1f8eb31441e2","tid":583843,"uid":18607,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime